you. So, Rachel, if someone was actually interested in, like, trying to test out Connect for their own

01:10:42.080 --> 01:10:50.160
org, what would they do? Yes, so you can definitely test out Connect for your organization as well,

01:10:50.160 --> 01:10:57.279
and I could put the link in the chat to help set up a call with our team so they learn more about

01:10:57.279 --> 01:11:03.120
your use case and talk to you about what you're trying to do, and I'll put that in the YouTube

