and then if you were going to, say, use AWS or GCP, you take that Dockerfile and then build it

01:12:28.399 --> 01:12:37.200
using the container building service of your cloud platform of choice and put it in your registry

01:12:37.200 --> 01:12:46.319
where it goes. Awesome. I know we're getting to about 15 minutes past the top of the hour.

